N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4627.8 - How papers may be filed

State Regulations

Filing of the foregoing papers with the commission at the
commission's office at 354 Broadway, Schenectady, NY 12305, may be either by
personal service or by certified mail, return receipt
requested. Notes
